data.text:
WPWR (105.1 MHz), better known by its branding "POWER 105.1", is an Urban Contemporary radio station in New York City, New York. The station is owned by Studio Networks, and broadcasts from studios in Manhattan with its radio and TV sisters. Its transmitter is located atop Empire State Building.
